#. <section class="sutta" id="dn20"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "dn20:0.1"
msgid "Dīgha Nikāya 20"
msgstr "Long Discourses 20"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "dn20:0.2"
msgid "Mahāsamayasutta"
msgstr "The Great Congregation"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs1"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.253"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

msgctxt "dn20:1.2"
msgid ""
"ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sakkesu viharati kapilavatthusmiṃ mahāvane mahatā "
"bhikkhusaṃghena saddhiṃ pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi sabbeheva arahantehi;"
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Sakyans, near "
"Kapilavatthu in the Great Wood, together with a large Saṅgha of around five "
"hundred mendicants, all of whom were perfected ones."

msgctxt "dn20:1.3"
msgid ""
"dasahi ca lokadhātūhi devatā yebhuyyena sannipatitā honti bhagavantaṃ "
"dassanāya bhikkhusaṃghañca."
msgstr ""
"And most of the deities from ten solar systems had gathered to see the "
"Buddha and the Saṅgha of mendicants."

#. VAR: devatānaṃ → devānaṃ (s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "dn20:1.4"
msgid "Atha kho catunnaṃ suddhāvāsakāyikānaṃ devatānaṃ etadahosi:"
msgstr ""
"Then four deities of the Pure Abodes, aware of what was happening, thought:"

msgctxt "dn20:1.5"
msgid ""
"“ayaṃ kho bhagavā sakkesu viharati kapilavatthusmiṃ mahāvane mahatā "
"bhikkhusaṃghena saddhiṃ pañcamattehi bhikkhusatehi sabbeheva arahantehi;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn20:1.6"
msgid ""
"dasahi ca lokadhātūhi devatā yebhuyyena sannipatitā honti bhagavantaṃ "
"dassanāya bhikkhusaṃghañca."
msgstr ""

#. VAR: paccekaṃ gāthaṃ → paccekagāthā (si) | paccekagāthaṃ (s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "dn20:1.7"
msgid ""
"Yannūna mayampi yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkameyyāma; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavato "
"santike paccekaṃ gāthaṃ bhāseyyāmā”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Why don’t we go to the Buddha and each recite a verse in his presence?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs3"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.254"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:3.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho tā devatā seyyathāpi nāma balavā puriso samiñjitaṃ vā bāhaṃ "
"pasāreyya pasāritaṃ vā bāhaṃ samiñjeyya; evameva—suddhāvāsesu devesu "
"antarahitā bhagavato purato pāturahesuṃ."
msgstr ""
"Then, as easily as a strong person would extend or contract their arm, they "
"vanished from the Pure Abodes and reappeared in front of the Buddha."

msgctxt "dn20:3.2"
msgid "Atha kho tā devatā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhaṃsu."
msgstr "They bowed to the Buddha and stood to one side."

msgctxt "dn20:3.3"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho ekā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Standing to one side, one deity recited this verse in the Buddha’s presence:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:3.4"
msgid "“Mahāsamayo pavanasmiṃ,"
msgstr "“There’s a great congregation in the woods,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:3.5"
msgid "Devakāyā samāgatā;"
msgstr "a host of gods have assembled."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:3.6"
msgid "Āgatamha imaṃ dhammasamayaṃ,"
msgstr "We’ve come to this righteous congregation"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:3.7"
msgid "Dakkhitāye aparājitasaṅghan”ti."
msgstr "to see the invincible Saṅgha!”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:3.8"
msgid "Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi:"
msgstr "Then another deity recited this verse in the Buddha’s presence:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:3.9"
msgid "“Tatra bhikkhavo samādahaṃsu,"
msgstr "“The mendicants there are immersed in samādhi,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: ujukaṃ akaṃsu → ujukamakaṃsu (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "dn20:3.10"
msgid "Cittamattano ujukaṃ akaṃsu;"
msgstr "they’ve straightened out their own minds."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:3.11"
msgid "Sārathīva nettāni gahetvā,"
msgstr "Like a charioteer who has taken the reins,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:3.12"
msgid "Indriyāni rakkhanti paṇḍitā”ti."
msgstr "the astute ones protect their senses.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:3.13"
msgid "Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi:"
msgstr "Then another deity recited this verse in the Buddha’s presence:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:3.14"
msgid "“Chetvā khīlaṃ chetvā palighaṃ,"
msgstr "“Having cut the stake and cut the bar,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: ūhacca → ohacca (s1-3, km) | uhacca (mr)
msgctxt "dn20:3.15"
msgid "Indakhīlaṃ ūhacca manejā;"
msgstr "they’re unmoved, with boundary post uprooted."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:3.16"
msgid "Te caranti suddhā vimalā,"
msgstr "They live pure and stainless,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:3.17"
msgid "Cakkhumatā sudantā susunāgā”ti."
msgstr "the young dragons tamed by the seer.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.255"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:3.18"
msgid "Atha kho aparā devatā bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi:"
msgstr "Then another deity recited this verse in the Buddha’s presence:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:3.19"
msgid "“Ye keci buddhaṃ saraṇaṃ gatāse,"
msgstr "“Anyone who has gone to the Buddha for refuge"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:3.20"
msgid "Na te gamissanti apāyabhūmiṃ;"
msgstr "won’t go to a plane of loss."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:3.21"
msgid "Pahāya mānusaṃ dehaṃ,"
msgstr "After giving up this human body,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:3.22"
msgid "Devakāyaṃ paripūressantī”ti."
msgstr "they swell the hosts of gods.”"

#. </p></blockquote><h2>
msgctxt "dn20:3.23"
msgid "1. Devatāsannipāta"
msgstr "1. The Gathering of Deities"

#. </h2><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs4"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:4.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "Then the Buddha said to the mendicants:"

#. VAR: honti → idaṃ padaṃ pts1 potthake
msgctxt "dn20:4.2"
msgid ""
"“yebhuyyena, bhikkhave, dasasu lokadhātūsu devatā sannipatitā honti, "
"tathāgataṃ dassanāya bhikkhusaṃghañca."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, most of the deities from ten solar systems have gathered to see "
"the Realized One and the mendicant Saṅgha."

#. VAR: etapparamāyeva → etaparamāyeva (si, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "dn20:4.3"
msgid ""
"Yepi te, bhikkhave, ahesuṃ atītamaddhānaṃ arahanto sammāsambuddhā, tesampi "
"bhagavantānaṃ etapparamāyeva devatā sannipatitā ahesuṃ seyyathāpi mayhaṃ "
"etarahi."
msgstr ""
"The Buddhas of the past had, and the Buddhas of the future will have, "
"gatherings of deities that are at most like the gathering for me now."

msgctxt "dn20:4.4"
msgid ""
"Yepi te, bhikkhave, bhavissanti anāgatamaddhānaṃ arahanto sammāsambuddhā, "
"tesampi bhagavantānaṃ etapparamāyeva devatā sannipatitā bhavissanti "
"seyyathāpi mayhaṃ etarahi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "dn20:4.5"
msgid "Ācikkhissāmi, bhikkhave, devakāyānaṃ nāmāni;"
msgstr "I shall declare the names of the heavenly hosts;"

msgctxt "dn20:4.6"
msgid "kittayissāmi, bhikkhave, devakāyānaṃ nāmāni;"
msgstr "I shall extol the names of the heavenly hosts;"

msgctxt "dn20:4.7"
msgid "desessāmi, bhikkhave, devakāyānaṃ nāmāni."
msgstr "I shall teach the names of the heavenly hosts."

msgctxt "dn20:4.8"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasikarotha, bhāsissāmī”ti."
msgstr "Listen and pay close attention, I will speak.”"

msgctxt "dn20:4.9"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ."
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” they replied."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:4.10"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said this:"

# anukassami isn’t anukaroti as per PTS dict, but anu-kasati = anu + √kṛṣ as per CPD, see http://sanskritdictionary.com/anukar%E1%B9%A3a%E1%B8%A5/1647/4
#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs5"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:5.1"
msgid "“Silokamanukassāmi,"
msgstr "“I shall invoke a paean of praise!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:5.2"
msgid "yattha bhummā tadassitā;"
msgstr "Where the earth-gods dwell,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:5.3"
msgid "Ye sitā girigabbharaṃ,"
msgstr "there, in mountain caves,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:5.4"
msgid "pahitattā samāhitā."
msgstr "resolute and composed,"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:5.5"
msgid "Puthūsīhāva sallīnā,"
msgstr "dwell many like lonely lions,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:5.6"
msgid "lomahaṃsābhisambhuno;"
msgstr "who have mastered their fears."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:5.7"
msgid "Odātamanasā suddhā,"
msgstr "Their minds are bright and pure,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:5.8"
msgid "vippasannamanāvilā."
msgstr "clear and undisturbed.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.256"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:5.9"
msgid "Bhiyyo pañcasate ñatvā,"
msgstr "The teacher knew that over five hundred"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:5.10"
msgid "vane kāpilavatthave;"
msgstr "were in the wood at Kapilavatthu."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:5.11"
msgid "Tato āmantayī satthā,"
msgstr "Therefore he addressed"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:5.12"
msgid "sāvake sāsane rate."
msgstr "the disciples who love the teaching:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:5.13"
msgid "‘Devakāyā abhikkantā,"
msgstr "“The heavenly hosts have come forth;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:5.14"
msgid "te vijānātha bhikkhavo’;"
msgstr "mendicants, you should be aware of them.”"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:5.15"
msgid "Te ca ātappamakaruṃ,"
msgstr "Those monks became keen,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:5.16"
msgid "sutvā buddhassa sāsanaṃ."
msgstr "hearing the Buddha’s instruction."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs6"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc16"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:6.1"
msgid "Tesaṃ pāturahu ñāṇaṃ,"
msgstr "Knowledge manifested in them,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:6.2"
msgid "amanussānadassanaṃ;"
msgstr "seeing those non-human beings."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:6.3"
msgid "Appeke satamaddakkhuṃ,"
msgstr "Some saw a hundred,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:6.4"
msgid "sahassaṃ atha sattariṃ."
msgstr "a thousand, even seventy thousand,"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc17"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:6.5"
msgid "Sataṃ eke sahassānaṃ,"
msgstr "while some saw a hundred thousand"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:6.6"
msgid "amanussānamaddasuṃ;"
msgstr "non-human beings."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:6.7"
msgid "Appekenantamaddakkhuṃ,"
msgstr "But some saw an endless number"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:6.8"
msgid "disā sabbā phuṭā ahuṃ."
msgstr "spread out in every direction."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc18"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:6.9"
msgid "Tañca sabbaṃ abhiññāya,"
msgstr "And all that was known"

#. <br>
#. VAR: vavatthitvāna → vavakkhitvāna (s1-3, km, pts1) | avekkhitvāna (ṭīkā)
msgctxt "dn20:6.10"
msgid "vavatthitvāna cakkhumā;"
msgstr "and distinguished by the Seer."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:6.11"
msgid "Tato āmantayī satthā,"
msgstr "Therefore he addressed"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:6.12"
msgid "sāvake sāsane rate."
msgstr "the disciples who love the teaching:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc19"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:6.13"
msgid "‘Devakāyā abhikkantā,"
msgstr "“The heavenly hosts have come forth;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:6.14"
msgid "te vijānātha bhikkhavo;"
msgstr "mendicants, you should be aware of them."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:6.15"
msgid "Ye vohaṃ kittayissāmi,"
msgstr "I shall extol them for you,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:6.16"
msgid "girāhi anupubbaso’."
msgstr "with lyrics in proper order."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs7"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc20"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:7.1"
msgid "Sattasahassā te yakkhā,"
msgstr "There are seven thousand spirits,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:7.2"
msgid "bhummā kāpilavatthavā;"
msgstr "earth-gods of Kapilavatthu."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:7.3"
msgid "Iddhimanto jutimanto,"
msgstr "They’re powerful and brilliant,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:7.4"
msgid "vaṇṇavanto yasassino;"
msgstr "so beautiful and glorious."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:7.5"
msgid "Modamānā abhikkāmuṃ,"
msgstr "Rejoicing, they’ve come forth"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:7.6"
msgid "bhikkhūnaṃ samitiṃ vanaṃ."
msgstr "to the meeting of mendicants in the wood."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc21"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:7.7"
msgid "Chasahassā hemavatā,"
msgstr "From the Himalayas there are six thousand"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:7.8"
msgid "yakkhā nānattavaṇṇino;"
msgstr "spirits of different colors."

#. <br>
#. VAR: jutimanto → jutīmanto (pts1)
msgctxt "dn20:7.9"
msgid "Iddhimanto jutimanto,"
msgstr "They’re powerful and brilliant,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:7.10"
msgid "vaṇṇavanto yasassino;"
msgstr "so beautiful and glorious."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:7.11"
msgid "Modamānā abhikkāmuṃ,"
msgstr "Rejoicing, they’ve come forth"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:7.12"
msgid "bhikkhūnaṃ samitiṃ vanaṃ."
msgstr "to the meeting of mendicants in the wood."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc22"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:7.13"
msgid "Sātāgirā tisahassā,"
msgstr "From Sātāgira there are three thousand"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:7.14"
msgid "yakkhā nānattavaṇṇino;"
msgstr "spirits of different colors."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:7.15"
msgid "Iddhimanto jutimanto,"
msgstr "They’re powerful and brilliant,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:7.16"
msgid "vaṇṇavanto yasassino;"
msgstr "so beautiful and glorious."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:7.17"
msgid "Modamānā abhikkāmuṃ,"
msgstr "Rejoicing, they’ve come forth"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:7.18"
msgid "bhikkhūnaṃ samitiṃ vanaṃ."
msgstr "to the meeting of mendicants in the wood."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc23"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:7.19"
msgid "Iccete soḷasasahassā,"
msgstr "And thus there are sixteen thousand"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:7.20"
msgid "yakkhā nānattavaṇṇino;"
msgstr "spirits of different colors."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:7.21"
msgid "Iddhimanto jutimanto,"
msgstr "They’re powerful and brilliant,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:7.22"
msgid "vaṇṇavanto yasassino;"
msgstr "so beautiful and glorious."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:7.23"
msgid "Modamānā abhikkāmuṃ,"
msgstr "Rejoicing, they’ve come forth"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:7.24"
msgid "bhikkhūnaṃ samitiṃ vanaṃ."
msgstr "to the meeting of mendicants in the wood."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs8"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.257"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc24"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:8.1"
msgid "Vessāmittā pañcasatā,"
msgstr "From Vessamittā there are five hundred"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:8.2"
msgid "yakkhā nānattavaṇṇino;"
msgstr "spirits of different colors."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:8.3"
msgid "Iddhimanto jutimanto,"
msgstr "They’re powerful and brilliant,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:8.4"
msgid "vaṇṇavanto yasassino;"
msgstr "so beautiful and glorious."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:8.5"
msgid "Modamānā abhikkāmuṃ,"
msgstr "Rejoicing, they’ve come forth"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:8.6"
msgid "bhikkhūnaṃ samitiṃ vanaṃ."
msgstr "to the meeting of mendicants in the wood."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc25"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:8.7"
msgid "Kumbhīro rājagahiko,"
msgstr "And there’s Kumbhīra of Rājagaha,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:8.8"
msgid "vepullassa nivesanaṃ;"
msgstr "whose home is on Mount Vepulla."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:8.9"
msgid "Bhiyyo naṃ satasahassaṃ,"
msgstr "Attended by more than"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:8.10"
msgid "yakkhānaṃ payirupāsati;"
msgstr "a hundred thousand spirits,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:8.11"
msgid "Kumbhīro rājagahiko,"
msgstr "Kumbhīra of Rājagaha"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:8.12"
msgid "sopāgā samitiṃ vanaṃ."
msgstr "also came to the meeting in the wood."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs9"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc26"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:9.1"
msgid "Purimañca disaṃ rājā,"
msgstr "King Dhataraṭṭha rules"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.2"
msgid "dhataraṭṭho pasāsati;"
msgstr "the eastern quarter."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.3"
msgid "Gandhabbānaṃ adhipati,"
msgstr "Lord of the fairies,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.4"
msgid "mahārājā yasassiso."
msgstr "he’s a great king, glorious."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc27"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:9.5"
msgid "Puttāpi tassa bahavo,"
msgstr "And he has many mighty sons"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.6"
msgid "indanāmā mahabbalā;"
msgstr "all of them named Inda."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.7"
msgid "Iddhimanto jutimanto,"
msgstr "They’re powerful and brilliant,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.8"
msgid "vaṇṇavanto yasassino;"
msgstr "so beautiful and glorious."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.9"
msgid "Modamānā abhikkāmuṃ,"
msgstr "Rejoicing, they’ve come forth"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.10"
msgid "bhikkhūnaṃ samitiṃ vanaṃ."
msgstr "to the meeting of mendicants in the wood."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc28"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:9.11"
msgid "Dakkhiṇañca disaṃ rājā,"
msgstr "King Virūḷha rules"

#. <br>
#. VAR: taṃ pasāsati → tappasāsati (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "dn20:9.12"
msgid "virūḷho taṃ pasāsati;"
msgstr "the southern quarter."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.13"
msgid "Kumbhaṇḍānaṃ adhipati,"
msgstr "Lord of the goblins,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.14"
msgid "mahārājā yasassiso."
msgstr "he’s a great king, glorious."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc29"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:9.15"
msgid "Puttāpi tassa bahavo,"
msgstr "And he has many mighty sons"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.16"
msgid "indanāmā mahabbalā;"
msgstr "all of them named Inda."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.17"
msgid "Iddhimanto jutimanto,"
msgstr "They’re powerful and brilliant,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.18"
msgid "vaṇṇavanto yasassino;"
msgstr "so beautiful and glorious."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.19"
msgid "Modamānā abhikkāmuṃ,"
msgstr "Rejoicing, they’ve come forth"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.20"
msgid "bhikkhūnaṃ samitiṃ vanaṃ."
msgstr "to the meeting of mendicants in the wood."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc30"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:9.21"
msgid "Pacchimañca disaṃ rājā,"
msgstr "King Virūpakkha rules"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.22"
msgid "virūpakkho pasāsati;"
msgstr "the western quarter."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.23"
msgid "Nāgānañca adhipati,"
msgstr "Lord of the dragons,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.24"
msgid "mahārājā yasassiso."
msgstr "he’s a great king, glorious."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.258"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc31"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:9.25"
msgid "Puttāpi tassa bahavo,"
msgstr "And he has many mighty sons"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.26"
msgid "indanāmā mahabbalā;"
msgstr "all of them named Inda."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.27"
msgid "Iddhimanto jutimanto,"
msgstr "They’re powerful and brilliant,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.28"
msgid "vaṇṇavanto yasassino;"
msgstr "so beautiful and glorious."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.29"
msgid "Modamānā abhikkāmuṃ,"
msgstr "Rejoicing, they’ve come forth"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.30"
msgid "bhikkhūnaṃ samitiṃ vanaṃ."
msgstr "to the meeting of mendicants in the wood."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc32"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:9.31"
msgid "Uttarañca disaṃ rājā,"
msgstr "King Kuvera rules"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.32"
msgid "kuvero taṃ pasāsati;"
msgstr "the northern quarter."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.33"
msgid "Yakkhānañca adhipati,"
msgstr "Lord of spirits,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.34"
msgid "mahārājā yasassiso."
msgstr "he’s a great king, glorious."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc33"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:9.35"
msgid "Puttāpi tassa bahavo,"
msgstr "And he has many mighty sons"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.36"
msgid "indanāmā mahabbalā;"
msgstr "all of them named Inda."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.37"
msgid "Iddhimanto jutimanto,"
msgstr "They’re powerful and brilliant,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.38"
msgid "vaṇṇavanto yasassino;"
msgstr "so beautiful and glorious."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.39"
msgid "Modamānā abhikkāmuṃ,"
msgstr "Rejoicing, they’ve come forth"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.40"
msgid "bhikkhūnaṃ samitiṃ vanaṃ."
msgstr "to the meeting of mendicants in the wood."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc34"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:9.41"
msgid "Purimaṃ disaṃ dhataraṭṭho,"
msgstr "Dhataraṭṭha in the east,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.42"
msgid "dakkhiṇena virūḷhako;"
msgstr "Virūḷhaka to the south,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.43"
msgid "Pacchimena virūpakkho,"
msgstr "Virūpakkha to the west,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.44"
msgid "kuvero uttaraṃ disaṃ."
msgstr "and Kuvera in the north."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc35"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:9.45"
msgid "Cattāro te mahārājā,"
msgstr "These Four Great Kings,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.46"
msgid "samantā caturo disā;"
msgstr "all around in the four quarters,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: Daddallamānā → daddaḷhamānā (mr)
msgctxt "dn20:9.47"
msgid "Daddallamānā aṭṭhaṃsu,"
msgstr "stood there dazzling"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:9.48"
msgid "vane kāpilavatthave."
msgstr "in the wood at Kapilavatthu."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs10"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc36"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:10.1"
msgid "Tesaṃ māyāvino dāsā,"
msgstr "Their deceitful bondservants came,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: āguṃ → āgū (s1-3, km) | āgu (pts1)
msgctxt "dn20:10.2"
msgid "āguṃ vañcanikā saṭhā;"
msgstr "so treacherous and crafty—"

# Speelings in this text follow Anandajoti’s translation of this text, http://www.ancient-buddhist-texts.net/Texts-and-Translations/Safeguard/02x-Atirekani-Sattasuttani-23.htm
#. <br>
#. VAR: viṭeṇḍu → veṭeṇḍu (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "dn20:10.3"
msgid "Māyā kuṭeṇḍu viṭeṇḍu,"
msgstr "the deceivers Kuṭeṇḍu, Viṭeṇḍu,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: viṭucca → viṭū ca (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "dn20:10.4"
msgid "viṭucca viṭuṭo saha."
msgstr "with Viṭucca and Viṭuḍa."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc37"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:10.5"
msgid "Candano kāmaseṭṭho ca,"
msgstr "And Candana and Kāmaseṭṭha,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: kinnighaṇḍu → kinnughaṇḍu (s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "dn20:10.6"
msgid "kinnighaṇḍu nighaṇḍu ca;"
msgstr "Kinnughaṇḍu and Nighaṇḍu,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:10.7"
msgid "Panādo opamañño ca,"
msgstr "Panāda and Opamañña,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:10.8"
msgid "devasūto ca mātali."
msgstr "and Mātali, the god’s charioteer."

# Comm has “Cittasenoti citto ca seno ca cittaseno ca” but given the singular this seems unlikely.
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc38"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:10.9"
msgid "Cittaseno ca gandhabbo,"
msgstr "Cittasena the fairy came too,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: janesabho → janosabho (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "dn20:10.10"
msgid "naḷorājā janesabho;"
msgstr "and the kings Nala and Janesabha,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:10.11"
msgid "Āgā pañcasikho ceva,"
msgstr "as well as Pañcasikha,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: sūriyavacchasā → suriyavaccasā (bj, pts1) | suriyavacchasā (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "dn20:10.12"
msgid "timbarū sūriyavacchasā."
msgstr "Timbaru, and Suriyavaccasā."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc39"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:10.13"
msgid "Ete caññe ca rājāno,"
msgstr "These and other kings there were,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:10.14"
msgid "gandhabbā saha rājubhi;"
msgstr "the fairies with their kings."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:10.15"
msgid "Modamānā abhikkāmuṃ,"
msgstr "Rejoicing, they’ve come forth"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:10.16"
msgid "bhikkhūnaṃ samitiṃ vanaṃ."
msgstr "to the meeting of mendicants in the wood."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs11"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc40"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:11.1"
msgid "Athāguṃ nāgasā nāgā,"
msgstr "Then came dragons from Nābhasa,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:11.2"
msgid "vesālā sahatacchakā;"
msgstr "and Vesālī, with the Tacchakas."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:11.3"
msgid "Kambalassatarā āguṃ,"
msgstr "The Kambalas and Assataras came"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:11.4"
msgid "pāyāgā saha ñātibhi."
msgstr "from Pāyāga with their kin."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc41"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:11.5"
msgid "Yāmunā dhataraṭṭhā ca,"
msgstr "From Yamunā the Dhataraṭṭha"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:11.6"
msgid "āgū nāgā yasassino;"
msgstr "dragons came, so glorious."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:11.7"
msgid "Erāvaṇo mahānāgo,"
msgstr "And Erāvaṇa the great dragon"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:11.8"
msgid "sopāgā samitiṃ vanaṃ."
msgstr "also came to the meeting in the wood."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.259"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc42"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:11.9"
msgid "Ye nāgarāje sahasā haranti,"
msgstr "Those who seize the dragon kings by force—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:11.10"
msgid "Dibbā dijā pakkhi visuddhacakkhū;"
msgstr "divine, twice-born birds with piercing vision—"

#. <br>
#. VAR: Vehāyasā → vehāsayā (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "dn20:11.11"
msgid "Vehāyasā te vanamajjhapattā,"
msgstr "swoop down to the wood from the sky;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:11.12"
msgid "Citrā supaṇṇā iti tesa nāmaṃ."
msgstr "their name is ‘Rainbow Phoenix’."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc43"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:11.13"
msgid "Abhayaṃ tadā nāgarājānamāsi,"
msgstr "But the dragon kings remained fearless,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:11.14"
msgid "Supaṇṇato khemamakāsi buddho;"
msgstr "for the Buddha kept them safe from the phoenixes."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:11.15"
msgid "Saṇhāhi vācāhi upavhayantā,"
msgstr "Introducing each other with gentle words,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:11.16"
msgid "Nāgā supaṇṇā saraṇamakaṃsu buddhaṃ."
msgstr "the dragons and phoenixes took the Buddha as their refuge."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs12"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc44"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:12.1"
msgid "Jitā vajirahatthena,"
msgstr "Defeated by Vajirahattha,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:12.2"
msgid "samuddaṃ asurāsitā;"
msgstr "the demons live in the ocean."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:12.3"
msgid "Bhātaro vāsavassete,"
msgstr "They’re brothers of Vāsava,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:12.4"
msgid "iddhimanto yasassino."
msgstr "powerful and glorious."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc45"></a>
#. VAR: Kālakañcā mahābhismā → kālakañjā mahābhismā (bj, s1-3) | kālakañjā mahābhiṃsā (pts1)
msgctxt "dn20:12.5"
msgid "Kālakañcā mahābhismā,"
msgstr "There’s the terrifying Kālakañjas,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:12.6"
msgid "asurā dānaveghasā;"
msgstr "the Dānaveghasa demons,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:12.7"
msgid "Vepacitti sucitti ca,"
msgstr "Vepacitti and Sucitti,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:12.8"
msgid "pahārādo namucī saha."
msgstr "Pahārāda with Namuci,"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc46"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:12.9"
msgid "Satañca baliputtānaṃ,"
msgstr "and a hundred of Bali’s sons,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:12.10"
msgid "sabbe verocanāmakā;"
msgstr "all named after Veroca."

#. <br>
#. VAR: balisenaṃ → baliṃ senaṃ (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "dn20:12.11"
msgid "Sannayhitvā balisenaṃ,"
msgstr "Bali’s army armed themselves"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:12.12"
msgid "rāhubhaddamupāgamuṃ;"
msgstr "and went up to the auspicious Rāhu, saying:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:12.13"
msgid "‘Samayo dāni bhaddante,"
msgstr "‘Now is the time, sir,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:12.14"
msgid "bhikkhūnaṃ samitiṃ vanaṃ’."
msgstr "for the meeting of mendicants in the wood.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs13"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc47"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:13.1"
msgid "Āpo ca devā pathavī,"
msgstr "The gods of Water and Earth,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:13.2"
msgid "tejo vāyo tadāgamuṃ;"
msgstr "and Fire and Wind came there."

#. <br>
#. VAR: vāraṇā → vāruṇā (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "dn20:13.3"
msgid "Varuṇā vāraṇā devā,"
msgstr "The Varuṇa and Vāruṇa gods,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:13.4"
msgid "somo ca yasasā saha."
msgstr "and Soma together with Yasa."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc48"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:13.5"
msgid "Mettā karuṇā kāyikā,"
msgstr "A host of the gods of Love"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:13.6"
msgid "āguṃ devā yasassino;"
msgstr "and Compassion came, so glorious."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:13.7"
msgid "Dasete dasadhā kāyā,"
msgstr "These ten hosts of gods"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:13.8"
msgid "sabbe nānattavaṇṇino."
msgstr "shone in all different colors."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc49"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:13.9"
msgid "Iddhimanto jutimanto,"
msgstr "They’re powerful and brilliant,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:13.10"
msgid "vaṇṇavanto yasassino;"
msgstr "so beautiful and glorious."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:13.11"
msgid "Modamānā abhikkāmuṃ,"
msgstr "Rejoicing, they’ve come forth"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:13.12"
msgid "bhikkhūnaṃ samitiṃ vanaṃ."
msgstr "to the meeting of mendicants in the wood."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs14"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc50"></a>
#. VAR: sahali ca → veṇhū ca devā sahalī ca (bj) | veṇḍū ca devā sahalī ca (s1-3, km) | veṇhū ca devā sahaḷī ca (pts1)
msgctxt "dn20:14.1"
msgid "Veṇḍudevā sahali ca,"
msgstr "The Veṇhu and Sahali gods,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:14.2"
msgid "asamā ca duve yamā;"
msgstr "and Asama, and the twin Yamas came."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:14.3"
msgid "Candassūpanisā devā,"
msgstr "The gods living on the moon came,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:14.4"
msgid "candamāguṃ purakkhatvā."
msgstr "with the Moon before them."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc51"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:14.5"
msgid "Sūriyassūpanisā devā,"
msgstr "The gods living on the sun came,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:14.6"
msgid "sūriyamāguṃ purakkhatvā;"
msgstr "with the Sun before them."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:14.7"
msgid "Nakkhattāni purakkhatvā,"
msgstr "And with the stars before them"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:14.8"
msgid "āguṃ mandavalāhakā."
msgstr "came the silly gods of clouds."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.260"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc52"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:14.9"
msgid "Vasūnaṃ vāsavo seṭṭho,"
msgstr "And Sakka came, the stronghold-giver,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:14.10"
msgid "sakkopāgā purindado;"
msgstr "known as Vāsava, the best of the Vasus."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:14.11"
msgid "Dasete dasadhā kāyā,"
msgstr "These ten hosts of gods"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:14.12"
msgid "sabbe nānattavaṇṇino."
msgstr "shone in all different colors."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc53"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:14.13"
msgid "Iddhimanto jutimanto,"
msgstr "They’re powerful and brilliant,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:14.14"
msgid "vaṇṇavanto yasassino;"
msgstr "so beautiful and glorious."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:14.15"
msgid "Modamānā abhikkāmuṃ,"
msgstr "Rejoicing, they’ve come forth"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:14.16"
msgid "bhikkhūnaṃ samitiṃ vanaṃ."
msgstr "to the meeting of mendicants in the wood."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs15"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc54"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:15.1"
msgid "Athāguṃ sahabhū devā,"
msgstr "Then came the Sahabhū gods,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:15.2"
msgid "jalamaggi sikhāriva;"
msgstr "blazing like a crested flame;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:15.3"
msgid "Ariṭṭhakā ca rojā ca,"
msgstr "and the Ariṭṭhakas and Rojas too,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:15.4"
msgid "umāpupphanibhāsino."
msgstr "and the gods hued blue as flax."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc55"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:15.5"
msgid "Varuṇā sahadhammā ca,"
msgstr "The Varuṇas and Sahadhammas,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:15.6"
msgid "accutā ca anejakā;"
msgstr "the Accutas and Anejakas,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:15.7"
msgid "Sūleyyarucirā āguṃ,"
msgstr "the Sūleyyas and Ruciras all came,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:15.8"
msgid "āguṃ vāsavanesino;"
msgstr "as did the Vāsavanesi gods."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:15.9"
msgid "Dasete dasadhā kāyā,"
msgstr "These ten hosts of gods"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:15.10"
msgid "sabbe nānattavaṇṇino."
msgstr "shone in all different colors."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc56"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:15.11"
msgid "Iddhimanto jutimanto,"
msgstr "They’re powerful and brilliant,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:15.12"
msgid "vaṇṇavanto yasassino;"
msgstr "so beautiful and glorious."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:15.13"
msgid "Modamānā abhikkāmuṃ,"
msgstr "Rejoicing, they’ve come forth"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:15.14"
msgid "bhikkhūnaṃ samitiṃ vanaṃ."
msgstr "to the meeting of mendicants in the wood."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs16"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc57"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:16.1"
msgid "Samānā mahāsamanā,"
msgstr "The Samānas, Mahāsamānas,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:16.2"
msgid "mānusā mānusuttamā;"
msgstr "Mānusas, and Mānusuttamas all came,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:16.3"
msgid "Khiḍḍāpadosikā āguṃ,"
msgstr "and the gods depraved by play,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:16.4"
msgid "āguṃ manopadosikā."
msgstr "and those who are malevolent."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc58"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:16.5"
msgid "Athāguṃ harayo devā,"
msgstr "Then came the Hari gods,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:16.6"
msgid "ye ca lohitavāsino;"
msgstr "and the Lohitavāsīs."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:16.7"
msgid "Pāragā mahāpāragā,"
msgstr "The Pāragas and Mahāpāragas came,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:16.8"
msgid "āguṃ devā yasassino;"
msgstr "such glorious gods."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:16.9"
msgid "Dasete dasadhā kāyā,"
msgstr "These ten hosts of gods"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:16.10"
msgid "sabbe nānattavaṇṇino."
msgstr "shone in all different colors."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc59"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:16.11"
msgid "Iddhimanto jutimanto,"
msgstr "They’re powerful and brilliant,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:16.12"
msgid "vaṇṇavanto yasassino;"
msgstr "so beautiful and glorious."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:16.13"
msgid "Modamānā abhikkāmuṃ,"
msgstr "Rejoicing, they’ve come forth"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:16.14"
msgid "bhikkhūnaṃ samitiṃ vanaṃ."
msgstr "to the meeting of mendicants in the wood."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs17"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc60"></a>
#. VAR: karambhā → karumhā (si, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "dn20:17.1"
msgid "Sukkā karambhā aruṇā,"
msgstr "The Sukkas, Karumhas, and Aruṇas"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:17.2"
msgid "āguṃ veghanasā saha;"
msgstr "came along with the Veghanasas."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:17.3"
msgid "Odātagayhā pāmokkhā,"
msgstr "And the Odātagayhas came as chiefs"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:17.4"
msgid "āguṃ devā vicakkhaṇā."
msgstr "of the Vicakkhaṇa gods."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc61"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:17.5"
msgid "Sadāmattā hāragajā,"
msgstr "The Sadāmattas and Hāragajas,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:17.6"
msgid "missakā ca yasassino;"
msgstr "and the glorious Missakas;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:17.7"
msgid "Thanayaṃ āga pajjunno,"
msgstr "Pajjuna came thundering,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:17.8"
msgid "yo disā abhivassati."
msgstr "he who rains on all quarters."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc62"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:17.9"
msgid "Dasete dasadhā kāyā,"
msgstr "These ten hosts of gods"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:17.10"
msgid "sabbe nānattavaṇṇino;"
msgstr "shone in all different colors."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:17.11"
msgid "Iddhimanto jutimanto,"
msgstr "They’re powerful and brilliant,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:17.12"
msgid "vaṇṇavanto yasassino;"
msgstr "so beautiful and glorious."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:17.13"
msgid "Modamānā abhikkāmuṃ,"
msgstr "Rejoicing, they’ve come forth"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:17.14"
msgid "bhikkhūnaṃ samitiṃ vanaṃ."
msgstr "to the meeting of mendicants in the wood."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs18"></a>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.261"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc63"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:18.1"
msgid "Khemiyā tusitā yāmā,"
msgstr "The Khemiyas, Tusitas, Yāmas,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:18.2"
msgid "kaṭṭhakā ca yasassino;"
msgstr "and the glorious Kaṭṭhakas came;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:18.3"
msgid "Lambītakā lāmaseṭṭhā,"
msgstr "The Lambītakas, Lāmaseṭṭhas,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:18.4"
msgid "jotināmā ca āsavā;"
msgstr "those called the Jotis and Āsavas."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:18.5"
msgid "Nimmānaratino āguṃ,"
msgstr "The Gods Who Love to Create came too,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:18.6"
msgid "athāguṃ paranimmitā."
msgstr "and those who delight in the Creations of Others."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc64"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:18.7"
msgid "Dasete dasadhā kāyā,"
msgstr "These ten hosts of gods"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:18.8"
msgid "sabbe nānattavaṇṇino;"
msgstr "shone in all different colors."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:18.9"
msgid "Iddhimanto jutimanto,"
msgstr "They’re powerful and brilliant,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:18.10"
msgid "vaṇṇavanto yasassino;"
msgstr "so beautiful and glorious."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:18.11"
msgid "Modamānā abhikkāmuṃ,"
msgstr "Rejoicing, they’ve come forth"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:18.12"
msgid "bhikkhūnaṃ samitiṃ vanaṃ."
msgstr "to the meeting of mendicants in the wood."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs19"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc65"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:19.1"
msgid "Saṭṭhete devanikāyā,"
msgstr "These sixty hosts of gods"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:19.2"
msgid "sabbe nānattavaṇṇino;"
msgstr "shone in all different colors."

#. <br>
#. VAR: āgacchuṃ → āgañchuṃ (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "dn20:19.3"
msgid "Nāmanvayena āgacchuṃ,"
msgstr "They came in order of their names,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:19.4"
msgid "ye caññe sadisā saha."
msgstr "these and others likewise, thinking:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc66"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:19.5"
msgid "‘Pavuṭṭhajātimakhilaṃ,"
msgstr "‘We shall see those rid of rebirth, kind,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:19.6"
msgid "oghatiṇṇamanāsavaṃ;"
msgstr "the undefiled ones who have crossed the flood,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:19.7"
msgid "Dakkhemoghataraṃ nāgaṃ,"
msgstr "and the dragon who brought them across,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:19.8"
msgid "candaṃva asitātigaṃ’."
msgstr "who like the Moon has overcome darkness.’"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs20"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc67"></a>
#. VAR: paramatto ca → paramattho ca (mr)
msgctxt "dn20:20.1"
msgid "Subrahmā paramatto ca,"
msgstr "Subrahmā and Paramatta came,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:20.2"
msgid "puttā iddhimato saha;"
msgstr "with sons of those powerful ones."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:20.3"
msgid "Sanaṅkumāro tisso ca,"
msgstr "Sanaṅkumāra and Tissa"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:20.4"
msgid "sopāga samitiṃ vanaṃ."
msgstr "also came to the meeting in the wood."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc68"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:20.5"
msgid "Sahassaṃ brahmalokānaṃ,"
msgstr "Of a thousand Brahmā realms,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:20.6"
msgid "mahābrahmābhitiṭṭhati;"
msgstr "the Great Brahmā stands forth."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:20.7"
msgid "Upapanno jutimanto,"
msgstr "He has arisen, resplendent,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:20.8"
msgid "bhismākāyo yasassiso."
msgstr "his formidable body so glorious."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc69"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:20.9"
msgid "Dasettha issarā āguṃ,"
msgstr "The ten Issarās came there,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:20.10"
msgid "paccekavasavattino;"
msgstr "each one of them wielding power,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:20.11"
msgid "Tesañca majjhato āga,"
msgstr "and in the middle of them came"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:20.12"
msgid "hārito parivārito."
msgstr "Hārita with his escorts.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs21"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc70"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:21.1"
msgid "Te ca sabbe abhikkante,"
msgstr "When they had all come forth—"

#. <br>
#. VAR: sainde → sinde (s1-3, km) | sainda (pts1)
msgctxt "dn20:21.2"
msgid "sainde deve sabrahmake;"
msgstr "the gods with their Lord, and the Brahmās—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:21.3"
msgid "Mārasenā abhikkāmi,"
msgstr "Māra’s army came forth too:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:21.4"
msgid "passa kaṇhassa mandiyaṃ."
msgstr "see the stupidity of the Dark Lord!"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.262"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc71"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:21.5"
msgid "‘Etha gaṇhatha bandhatha,"
msgstr "“Come, seize them and bind them,” he said,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:21.6"
msgid "rāgena baddhamatthu vo;"
msgstr "“let them be bound by desire!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:21.7"
msgid "Samantā parivāretha,"
msgstr "Surround them on all sides,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:21.8"
msgid "mā vo muñcittha koci naṃ’."
msgstr "don’t let any escape!”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc72"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:21.9"
msgid "Iti tattha mahāseno,"
msgstr "And so there the great general"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:21.10"
msgid "kaṇho senaṃ apesayi;"
msgstr "sent forth his dark army."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:21.11"
msgid "Pāṇinā talamāhacca,"
msgstr "He struck the ground with his fist"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:21.12"
msgid "saraṃ katvāna bheravaṃ."
msgstr "to make a horrifying sound"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc73"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:21.13"
msgid "Yathā pāvussako megho,"
msgstr "like a storm cloud shedding rain,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:21.14"
msgid "thanayanto savijjuko;"
msgstr "thundering and flashing."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:21.15"
msgid "Tadā so paccudāvatti,"
msgstr "But then he retreated,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: asayaṃvase → asayaṃvasī (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "dn20:21.16"
msgid "saṅkuddho asayaṃvase."
msgstr "furious, out of control."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-cs" id="pts-cs22"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc74"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:22.1"
msgid "Tañca sabbaṃ abhiññāya,"
msgstr "And all that was known"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:22.2"
msgid "vavatthitvāna cakkhumā;"
msgstr "and distinguished by the Seer."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:22.3"
msgid "Tato āmantayī satthā,"
msgstr "Therefore he addressed"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:22.4"
msgid "sāvake sāsane rate."
msgstr "the disciples who love the teaching:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc75"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:22.5"
msgid "‘Mārasenā abhikkantā,"
msgstr "“Māra’s army has arrived;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:22.6"
msgid "te vijānātha bhikkhavo’;"
msgstr "mendicants, you should be aware of them.”"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:22.7"
msgid "Te ca ātappamakaruṃ,"
msgstr "Those monks became keen,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:22.8"
msgid "sutvā buddhassa sāsanaṃ;"
msgstr "hearing the Buddha’s instruction."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:22.9"
msgid "Vītarāgehi pakkāmuṃ,"
msgstr "The army fled from those free of passion,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:22.10"
msgid "nesaṃ lomāpi iñjayuṃ."
msgstr "and not a single hair was stirred!"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc76"></a>
msgctxt "dn20:22.11"
msgid "‘Sabbe vijitasaṅgāmā,"
msgstr "“All are triumphant in battle,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:22.12"
msgid "bhayātītā yasassino;"
msgstr "so fearless and glorious."

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:22.13"
msgid "Modanti saha bhūtehi,"
msgstr "They rejoice with all the spirits,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "dn20:22.14"
msgid "sāvakā te janesutā’”ti."
msgstr "the disciples well-known among men.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "dn20:22.15"
msgid "Mahāsamayasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
